For each ke ∈ [0, 5], the amplitudes and phases of both theoretical and simulated Tf for the three values of a1 are plotted in Fig. 2c. Both theoretical and simulation results show that the amplitude is amplified at \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
